com.exacttarget.etpushsdk
Class ETAnalytics

java.lang.Object
  com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ETAnalytics

public class ETAnalytics
extends Object

Analytics engine for MobilePush. Add tracking code to each Activity in your application.

Usage:

 
 public class MyActivity extends Activity {
  ...
  @Override
  protected void onResume() {
    super.onResume();
    ETAnalytics.engine().activityResumed(this);
  }

  @Override
  protected void onPause() {
    super.onPause();
    ETAnalytics.engine().activityPaused(this);
  }
  ...
 }
